    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "次のMV撮影は夏の海で……\nわ、私の出番が多め、ですか！？",
      "startTime": 7.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 12.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、ど、どうしようっ\nわ、私でいいんでしょうか……？",
      "startTime": 15.7078105926514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 19.966666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。俺は各メンバーに\n前に出てもらいたいと思っているんだ",
      "startTime": 22.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、わ、分かりました\nどれくらい出来るか分かりませんけど……",
      "startTime": 29.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 32.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "せ、せせせ、精一杯頑張ります！",
      "startTime": 32.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage015",
      "startTime": 37.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage015",
      "startTime": 37.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、やっと今日の仕事が片付いたな\nん？　まだ誰か練習してるのか",
      "startTime": 43.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 48.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……っ\nこれくらいじゃ、まだぜんぜんダメ……っ",
      "startTime": 53.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3333333333358,
          "startTime": 56.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 57.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。まだ練習してたんだな",
      "startTime": 61.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "今回はなんだか\n練習しても練習しても不安になっちゃって",
      "startTime": 66.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "だから……本番まで少しでも詰めておきたいんです",
      "startTime": 70.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "気合が入ってるな\nそうだ、確か冷蔵庫にアレが……ちょっと待ってて",
      "startTime": 77.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 82.76666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "その手にあるのは……桃のゼリー！\nとっても美味しそう……",
      "startTime": 89.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　い、いけないいけない\nこんな時間に食べちゃったら……",
      "startTime": 95.0107527866158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いっぱい動いたしなぁ～\nちょっとくらいなら、でも、でも～",
      "startTime": 100.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、私をこんなに悩ませるなんて……\n{user}さんは意地悪です",
      "startTime": 109.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ってる時は好きなものを一杯食べた方がいいって\n遙子さんもよく言ってるだろ？",
      "startTime": 116.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、遙子さんは最近すっごく\n体重を気にしてましたよ？",
      "startTime": 121.233586011614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "う……程度によると思うぞ？\nほら、ひんやりしてるうちに食べた方がいい",
      "startTime": 127.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～……わ、分かりました\nそれでは、ありがたくいただきます",
      "startTime": 135.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～おっきい実が入ってる～あむっ",
      "startTime": 139.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "んふぅぅ～\nおいひぃぃ～",
      "startTime": 147.907864381328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！\nし、失礼しました、みっともない所を……",
      "startTime": 151.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ははっ、気にしなくていいって\n一休み出来たか？",
      "startTime": 158.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ありがとうございます\n…………",
      "startTime": 164.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……どうした？",
      "startTime": 165.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "あの、私……東京に出て来てから\n沢山のアイドルと出会いました",
      "startTime": 172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "そしていろんな人を見てきたからこそ\n月ストとサニピのみんなの凄さが改めて分かったんです",
      "startTime": 177.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "それに\nみんなどんどん前に進んでる気がするんです",
      "startTime": 183.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "そんな中で、少し個性の薄い自分に\n焦りを感じちゃって…",
      "startTime": 190.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今回のMVで私も前に進みたいんです",
      "startTime": 192.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "渚……",
      "startTime": 197.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "よーし！\nもうひと頑張りしていきます！",
      "startTime": 199.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "差し入れ、ありがとうございました！\n今日もお疲れ様です！",
      "startTime": 204.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、お疲れ様……\nあんまり無理はしないようにな？",
      "startTime": 208.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_01-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "startTime": 210.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
